-- Citi revises Q3 lower due to legal accruals
-- By Ankur Banerjee in Bangalore
-- Thu Oct 30, 2014 04:29PM EDT
-- None



Oct 30 (Reuters) - Citigroup Inc <C.N> revised its third-quarter results lower due to a $600 million increase in legal accruals.

The bank adjusted its third-quarter net income to $2.84 billion from $3.44 billion, citing "rapidly evolving regulatory inquiries and investigations".